se.miun.itm.input.model.param

Class ParamStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.miun.itm.input.model.param.ParamStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Identifiable

    public class ParamStore
extends java.lang.Object
implements Identifiable
    a The data-structure that manages all parameter related activities in InPUT. Every design space has a parameter store, to which it out-sources its initialization, parameter lookup, and data consistency control. The ParamStore makes sure that the mappings are bound correctly to the parameter definitions, and else report otherwise.
    Author:
    Felix Dobslaw
